<section class="test-show">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <h1 class="tests-para">Instructions: </h1> 

        <ol class="instructions-list">
        
            <li class="instructions-list-item">You will be presented a random piece of text based on your choice of difficulty.</li>
            <li class="instructions-list-item">Try your best to type blindly - dont look down at the keyboard!</li>
            <li class="instructions-list-item">If you make a mistake - keep going! Focus on correcting your mistakes after the test.</li>
            <li class="instructions-list-item">Timing will start as soon as you press the 'Begin Test' button.</li>
            <li class="instructions-list-item">No time limit.</li>
            <li class="instructions-list-item">Dont just copy and paste the text into the input field!</li>
        
        </ol>

        <%= button_to 'Begin Test', test_sessions_path, params: {:test_session => {test_id: @test.id, user_id: current_user.id}} %>
    </div>
</section>
